{"tid":474169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國男尿尿釀電力短路 電梯門打不開害到自己","createTime":"2017-11-20T02:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T04:29:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5c64ca73125fd1dd5e5dc2869dd4857b702268","tid":474169,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/100303_6b0f2389e326c8940d49b4e26d2c75e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F100303_6b0f2389e326c8940d49b4e26d2c75e2.jpg&h=bd2794c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國一名男子日前搭電梯時，因為想上廁所，直接解開褲頭對著電梯門狂尿，但這個舉動卻害到自己，電梯內的電力系統受到尿液影響短路，該名男子就被關在電梯裡了。<br />\n<br />\n該棟大樓管委會監視器畫面被民眾上傳至中國影音網站「秒拍」，從影片中可以清楚看見，一名男子進電梯後，先按下自己欲抵達的13樓，接著解開褲頭對著電梯門尿尿，此舉影響到電梯內部電力系統，右方的電梯樓層按鈕瞬間多亮了4個。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子在電梯門無故打開後，還不知道發生什麼事情，將門關上繼續搭乘電梯，直到電梯樓層按鈕燈號全滅，電梯亦停擺，他才發現事情大條，嘗試將門打開卻徒勞無功，許多台灣網友對影片內容表示，「中國人沒素質不意外」、「87分不能在高啦」、「沒漏電真幸運」、「沒墜樓算他好運」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/100337_caec82c504bc9e59e00e79b66dfe769e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F100337_caec82c504bc9e59e00e79b66dfe769e.jpg&h=34d45432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2258620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2258620&d=Q%2FzATyi%2BLt4M8DTUOBGFieargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8a54656b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2258620&h=c81b56ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2258620</a>"},{"pid":"ee1687f50fb2f831e6e24091cded8f41b0c0b168","tid":474169,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qulO4LE5jGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqulO4LE5jGw&d=Q%2FzATyi%2BLt4M8DTUOBGFieargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=85d23edc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qulO4LE5jGw</a>"},{"pid":"63b98bd7b02d16720ddfc0aa152afaa2ee69a287","tid":474169,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"中國嘢, 你唔搞佢都出事, 你重要搞破壞... 唔怪得成個國家咁多意外"},{"pid":"1b28c350c66215dbf3d743f446263a529ea0fdf7","tid":474169,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"f70cfbb3c4c28e747e1c44326ff6c10da2d4ff3a","tid":474169,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"87分不能在高啦"},{"pid":"175d67e55dc776f4717f3348dc578cd71dc87572","tid":474169,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"升降機內小便引短路　浙童開門逃生墮槽重傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/346456/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/346456/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解佢地成日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73eb923a8f9b13318ce46a7528bcfca43b3039db","tid":474169,"uid":71257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"諗極都唔明點解會有人係電梯到痾屎尿<br />\n<br />\n有時電梯仲會貼住請勿便溺嘅告示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84225031f4157011604840f24158948a3187e5c","tid":474169,"uid":60524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"唔柯埋屎先走算比面"}]}